Package com.bluegosling.function Description

Interfaces and classes that complement the standard java.util.function package. This includes new functional interfaces, like PartialFunction (and its kin) and numerous primitive specializations of standard interfaces (like BooleanBinaryOperator, FloatPredicate and ShortConsumer to name just a few).
